    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This chassis is paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS overhaul, ensuring the structural and mechanical integrity required for spirited driving. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing its original MacPherson/Multi-link configuration for exceptional lateral grip. While the aesthetics reflect a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the powertrain and drivetrain are optimized for immediate performance and reliability.",
