      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 2017 Executive Sport Sedan has been meticulously maintained and serves as a perfect balance of performance and daily usability. The exterior retains its deep, factory luster, though a keen eye will spot a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel rim consistent with careful city driving. Inside, the cabin remains a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium leather seats have been treated regularly and show only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, with no tears or fading. All electronics, from the responsive infotainment screen to the panoramic sunroof, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is in great shape, boasting a complete service log with the most recent oil change, fluid flush, and brake inspection performed just 1,500 miles ago. It rides on a set of high-performance all-season tires with plenty of tread depth remaining. Garage-kept and driven primarily on weekends, this car offers a reliable and spirited driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
